3. DISCORD DMCA TAKEDOWN PROCEDURE

If you believe a Discord bot, server, or user is infringing on this copyright
or using the "Onyx Development" brand without permission:

STEP 1: Gather evidence (screenshots, user IDs, server IDs)
STEP 2: File a DMCA Takedown Request with Discord:
        https://support.discord.com/hc/en-us/requests/new

STEP 3: Include the following information in your report:

• Your full name and contact information
• A description of the copyrighted work (Onyx Development bot)
• The specific location of the infringing content (Discord user ID/server ID)
• A statement under penalty of perjury that you are authorized to act on behalf of Onyx Development Pvt Ltd
• Your physical or electronic signature

Discord will typically respond within 2-7 business days.

